epending on the type of the store. The data is collected and sent to the backend in a format, that requires no additional preparation </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":407} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://wp-stone-lab/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/img_article_2-1024x522.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-407\"/><figcaption>Picture’s Name</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>title h3<br> </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The solution was found and now let’s take a close look at the process from the beginning till the end.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2> Title H2 </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The first meeting where our business analyst was discussing the task and deadlines with the company’s officials showed that a lot of work should be done to clear the goals and get the right understanding of the working process. Our expert had to interview all the stakeholders to get a clear idea of the working process and was able to find some problem areas in it, then the business vision was formulated.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote {\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<blockquote style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-default\"><p>There were quite a lot of stakeholders in the system (sales department managers, IT department managers, outlet agents) and our first aim was to meet all their requirements although they sometimes contradicted one another. Eventually, we were able to find the best solution that turned to be the most effective and suited everyone.</p><cite>Business Analyst</cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Title H2</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The first meeting where our business analyst was discussing the task and deadlines with the company’s officials showed that a lot of work should be do